{"tid":2000193,"cid":15,"subCid":0,"title":"其實買樓先係最穩健既投資","createTime":"2020-05-03T16:29:27.000Z","updateTime":"2020-05-04T03:58:56.000Z","uid":180204,"like":5,"dislike":11,"uniUserReply":12,"replies":[{"pid":"15bc859bef6b1c5c6a30d0e956a40fed8157745f","tid":2000193,"uid":180204,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-03T16:29:27.000Z","msg":"特別係人多地少既地區<br />\n<br />\n租金分分鐘佔唔少人入息1/3-1/2<br />\n<br />\n你有個單位租出去 都財務自由左一半<br />\n<br />\n淨低一半咪做啲想做又低人工既野 <br />\n<br />\n有一千萬，你做股票分分鐘一個浪都震走你1/3<br />\n拎去買樓就唔同<br />\n<br />\n開兩層樓 一自住 一放租 = 財務自由<br />\n<br />\n就係咁簡單<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n有老婆又肯搏啲既按多個單位出來都仲得<br />\n一齊供<br />\n<br />\n到有仔女又再按 第四個單位俾佢供<br />\n<br />\n咁你死左 你個仔就有4個單位 夠16歲已經可以日日開p 屌女<br />\n<br />\n俾你玩足一世股票都未必做到<img src=\"https://i-lih-kg.cdn.ampproject.org/ii/w68/s/i.lih.kg/540/http://n2.hk/d/images/smilies/default/smile_39.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fi-lih-kg.cdn.ampproject.org%2Fii%2Fw68%2Fs%2Fi.lih.kg%2F540%2Fhttp%3A%2F%2Fn2.hk%2Fd%2Fimages%2Fsmilies%2Fdefault%2Fsmile_39.gif&h=a4c4b70d&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"d1ecb14f940b581b4e71a37d1e237bf75105a33f","tid":2000193,"uid":114779,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-05-03T16:30:21.000Z","msg":"哪有錢"},{"pid":"bb02f41c1ec69ba4e6afea0699cd2a92252ebc3e","tid":2000193,"uid":180204,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"quote":{"pid":"d1ecb14f940b581b4e71a37d1e237bf75105a33f","tid":2000193,"uid":114779,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-05-03T16:30:21.000Z","msg":"哪有錢"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-03T16:32:32.000Z","msg":"咁就要玩牛熊 同 炒期油<br />\n<br />\n我都係咁起家"},{"pid":"a49890555a0254a460f097c95aa80be6d113cf4c","tid":2000193,"uid":349349,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-03T16:33:32.000Z","msg":"認同，最穩陣的大槓桿投資<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/8VknTOH.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F8VknTOH.jpg&h=74904072&s={SIZE}\" /><